  // ── Local Inference (LLamaSharp) ─────────────────────────────
  // In-process GGUF model inference via LLamaSharp (llama.cpp).
  // GpuLayerCount (default -1): layers offloaded to GPU. -1 = all. 0 = CPU only.
  //   Falls back to CPU gracefully when no GPU is available.
  // ContextSize (default 8192): context window in tokens.
  // KeepLoaded (default true): models stay resident after first use.
  //   Set false to auto-unload after IdleCooldownMinutes of inactivity.
  // IdleCooldownMinutes (default 5): idle time before unloading an
  //   unpinned model. Only applies when KeepLoaded is false.
  // ModelsDirectory (default <AppContext.BaseDirectory>/Models): root folder
  //   used by ModelDownloadManager for GGUF downloads/resume. Override to
  //   point at a shared/external SSD when you don't want models under the
  //   install directory. Path is created on first use.
  // HuggingFaceToken (default unset): personal access token sent as
  //   "Authorization: Bearer <token>" by HuggingFaceUrlResolver. Required
  //   for gated/private repos and raises HF anonymous rate limits.
